Catherine Rees, Head of Ecommerce at Numatic - the makers of the iconic Henry the Vacuum, will be joining us for an exclusive webinar, “From Dust to Data: Vacuuming Up Insights from Ecommerce’s Top Performers.” In partnership with GENE Commerce and Akoova, we’ll dive into the key takeaways from the eCommerce Insights & Strategies Report.

This report captures the voices of 50 senior leaders across retail, wholesale, distribution, and manufacturing,  spanning up-and-coming brands to global market leaders. Attendees can look forward to a lively discussion, evidence-based insights, and practical advice from experts and partners who navigate ecommerce challenges from every perspective.

? December 10 | 2 pm GMT
